  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and cook, stirring occasionally, until golden brown, about 10 minutes.",
    "Add garlic and ginger and cook, stirring constantly, for 1 minute.",
    "Add beef and cook, stirring occasionally, until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add cumin, coriander, cayenne pepper, salt, and black pepper and stir to combine.",
    "Add broth and vinegar, then bring to a boil.",
    "Cover the pot and transfer to the oven.",
    "Braise until the beef is tender and the sauce has thickened, about 2 1/2 hours.",
    "Stir in parsley and serve over rice or with warm pita bread."
